Description: An efficient sensitivity analysis for models based on 
    Monte Carlo samples. For a stress to an input / output, the (stressed)
    probabilty (meaure) scenario weights RE calculated by minimising 
    the Kullback-Leobler divergence with respect to the baseline
    model.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
